Constructor Detail

Performance

public Performance(int servers,
                   int clients,
                   int cacheSize,
                   java.lang.String strategy)
Class that can be used for scaled performance measurements. It requires an existing configuration file for the ECS with 10 server names. The constructor of this class sets up the performance testing framework.

Parameters:
servers - Number of servers
clients - Number of clients
cacheSize - Desired cacheSize on each server
strategy - Storage strategy
